                            <comment id="429695" author="adilger" created="Mon, 30 Sep 2024 22:00:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We are actually trying to increase the number of supported NIDs on the server to more than 32. Clients would be sent a maximum of 32 NIDs, but possibly fewer, based on the LNet network the client is connected to, and whether that LNet network is among the listed server NIDs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;is this current limitation being fixed in the client or server code? &#160;Is it possible to change this code to allow, say, 128-256 NIDs internally for a server?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
